traits.description:
Increase final damage by **18%**.

**Scattering Technique Enhancement**:

Water Gathering Enhancement: Increase all elemental damage by **20%**.

Surge Enhancement: When **Lunar Stars** are the active weapon, increase Surge's damage by **150%**, and when Altered Resonance is active, increase Surge's damage by an additional **100%**.

Wave Pressure Enhancement: Increase the damage of weapon skills and discharge by **45%**.

Vortex Enhancement: When dealing physical damage while the Vortex is active, increase final damage, up to **64%** (10 seconds to reach the max value).

Shackle Enhancement: When using Benediction Resonance, extend water prison's duration to **5** seconds and the basic resistance reduction effect is increased by **15%**.

Nourishing Spring Enhancement: When using Fortitude Resonance, increase resistance by (**max HP** / **50000**)%, up to **20%**.
